[30;1m54 | [0m[35m    top of the list. Selecting this choice will result in the `data` property[0m
[30;1m55 | [0m[35m    being `None`. The label for this blank choice can be set by specifying the[0m
[30;1m56 | [0m[35m    `blank_text` parameter.[0m
[30;1m57 | [0m[35m    """[0m

[30;1m21 | [0m[35mFlask-Admin is a batteries-included, simple-to-use[0m
[30;1m22 | [0m[35m[Flask](https://flask.palletsprojects.com/) extension that lets you add admin[0m
[30;1m23 | [0m[35minterfaces to Flask applications. It is inspired by the *django-admin*[0m
[30;1m24 | [0m[35mpackage, but implemented in such a way that the developer has total[0m
